```
func la_retain(_ object: la_object_t) -> la_object_t
```

Deprecated

This API is deprecated, please use BLAS and LAPACK

## [ Parameters ](/documentation/Accelerate/la_retain(_:)#parameters)

`object`The object to retain.

## [Return Value](/documentation/Accelerate/la_retain(_:)#return-value)

The retained object.

## [Discussion](/documentation/Accelerate/la_retain(_:)#discussion)

Increment the reference count of a la_object_t object.

On a platform with the modern Objective-C runtime this is exactly equivalent to sending the object the -[retain] message.
